<p><strong>William Faulkner: </strong>That's <span class="unclear tooltip" title="Text was unclear">[not all]</span>&mdash;making a verb out of a noun.</p>
<p><strong>Atcheson Hench: </strong>You did that yourself?</p>
<p><strong>William Faulkner: </strong>No. I've heard that.</p>
<p><strong>Atcheson Hench: </strong>Oh, I see.</p>
<p><strong>William Faulkner: </strong>That's&mdash;I imagine that that's in Georgia and Alabama, too.</p>
<hr>
<a name="wfaudio11_1.43">&nbsp;</a><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">
