<p><strong>William Faulkner: </strong>A hitch or a lead is snapped into the halter&mdash;tied to a
						<span class="unclear tooltip" title="Text was unclear">[bar]</span>.</p>
<hr>
<a name="wfaudio11_1.45">&nbsp;</a><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">
